= SDL_GetWindowMouseGrab =

Get a window's mouse grab mode.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
SDL_bool SDL_GetWindowMouseGrab(SDL_Window * window);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns This returns [[SDL_TRUE]] if mouse is grabbed, and [[SDL_FALSE]]
otherwise.

